metadata.description: A membership pass to CUD DAO gives you part ownership and voting rights towards the development of the platform and DAO. With this pass, you'll be able to shape the future of the DAO and have access to all the benefits that come with it! We allocate a % from the creator directly to our treasury safe controlled by the CUD DAO Maintainers
